 "AUTO COMMANDS:
 "auto expand tab to blanks
 "autocmd FileType c,cpp

 "Restore the last quit position when open file.

autocmd BufReadPost *
			\ if line("'\"") > 0 && line("'\"") <= line("$") |
			\     exe "normal g'\"" |
			\ endif
